title: Tuesday Pt2: Teams 'torn' about; Kyle & Jason's playoff teams; Power Rankings
itunes:title: Tuesday Pt2: Teams 'torn' about; Kyle & Jason's playoff teams; Power Rankings
description:
Part two of the Good Morning Football Podcast begins looking around the league and answering which team they’re torn on. Hosts Jamie Erdahl, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager, and Super Bowl Champion Jason McCourty throw out four different teams they’re unsure about. Next, Kyle and Jason reveal their NFC and AFC playoff teams and then the podcast finishes up with Dan Hanzus’ power rankings.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
